		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Not even the original developers attempted it.  Very few games were properly hacked.  Most developers didn't even bother to correct the music pitch.  Some corrected the music tempo, but not the pitch (RARE).
<br />
<br />Kudos to the Rygar developers for actually making a competent PAL version, gameplay speed wise.  Even though they still screwed up the sound pitch.

		

